	abstract = {STUDY OBJECTIVE: 8-Isoprostane is considered an index of oxidative stress. Measurement of 8-isoprostane in the expired breath condensate, a totally noninvasive method, has not been used to explore the level of inflammation in pulmonary sarcoidosis. Therefore, the aim of our study was to measure the levels of 8-isoprostane in the expired breath condensate of patients with sarcoidosis, and to investigate the relation of 8-isoprostane level to disease activity.
